{"tid":234333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔真係好低質羅，唔該","createTime":"2017-05-08T08:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T20:27:41.000Z","uid":77696,"like":50,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e0e10df445a3d5d0f7ae36cf23469cd2864002","tid":234333,"uid":77696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"前2日成班連登仔話搞咩5p網聚wo<br />\n我真係未聽過連登仔會去食m記咁cheap羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n500隻雞翼同亞古獸就收賣到班友，真係影衰哂「連登仔」3隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出到黎個個都係2隻眼1個口1個鼻羅，原來都係不外如是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由其果個咩「米高堅尼」，條毒撚我懷疑佢連150都唔知有無，又話連登仔個個180高嘅？底佢一世溝唔到女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有呀，條毒撚出心出力出錢搞，當自己大明星呀？又話要跳樓，又話呀爺入院（已死）都唔知博咩？好q嘔心羅唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40kiiC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40kiiC2.jpg&h=9fe1b69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重要個個最後話好溫馨，想搞多幾次？學肥絲大隻話齋，咁咪搞到你地個個開心羅！都唔知為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登仔love you all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，打錯，fuck you all先真<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90451f3a09f70dedba004a35404b5c3beb4b5953","tid":234333,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:35:48.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265c83c7b8d5c0038cfb88597e86f60b09960354","tid":234333,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"尼到系5p囉吾巧意思🙄"},{"pid":"89d06350c8274a93c0d243522ba6b2b79b428813","tid":234333,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:39:32.000Z","ms